{"tid":573842,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"同人唔同命？巴西與阿根廷人去中超的結局完全唔同","createTime":"2018-02-27T00:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T05:40:58.000Z","uid":3363,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"abc144a389f9fb97a279d65246011c6332684db0","tid":573842,"uid":3363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:24:17.000Z","msg":"雖然都係貪錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我發覺巴西同阿根廷人去中超好似結局都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴西：<br />\n柏圖 岩岩亞冠入波幫球隊追和<br />\n保連奴 番左去疤<br />\n奧斯卡 亞冠有出，keep住正選<br />\n候克 變左上海上港icon<br />\n<br />\n就算唔出名既球星：<br />\n艾傑臣 打滾中超好耐 有平穩表現<br />\n穆里奇 含大拎亞冠功臣之一<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷：<br />\n迪維斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呃錢球皇<br />\n拿維斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最出名係仆落廣告版之後失左蹤<br />\n孔卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好小小 但紀律都係唔得<br />\n<br />\n唔出名既球星：<br />\n就真係唔出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我廢到一個都up唔出<br />\n<br />\n黎緊馬斯又去埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎都唔會有咩好結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本阿根廷人性格都係有d問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9d5de02b4302b0468dbf874dcfd783ec854ef2","tid":573842,"uid":87072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:29:34.000Z","msg":"拿維斯上季入20球，同無女、高拉特並列射手榜第二名喎"},{"pid":"0636d4a50590a31b459f20cdfacd82e7ed1cbe25","tid":573842,"uid":54161,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:30:57.000Z","msg":"其實係泰維斯大仆街姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38527a9aafcae76f40f5501882ce704e54809b0c","tid":573842,"uid":90515,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:32:01.000Z","msg":"拎幾個個案就定論到一個國家嘅人嘅質素，樓主真中肯"},{"pid":"cd093f09d78682f8f2d